direction: down
vars: {
  d2-config: {
    layout-engine: elk
    theme-id: 4
  }
}
title: |md
  # Undo Order: Global LSN Priority Queue
  Multiple active transactions must be undone in **reverse LSN order globally**, not per-transaction.
| {near: top-center}
